name: Evolve Active Global Fixed Income Fund
longDescription: The Evolve Active Global Fixed Income Fund seeks to generate positive returns throughout the interest rate and economic cycles, first by allocating to different credit asset classes, and also through bottom¿up individual security selection. The Fund seeks to provide long term returns in excess of the 3 month U.S. dollar London Interbank Offered Rate (LIBOR) by investing primarily in global debt securities of corporate issuers. By allocating to different credit asset classes, and also through bottom-up individual security selection. The fund seeks to provide long term returns in excess of the 3 month U.S. dollar London Interbank Offered Rate by investing primarily in global debt securities of corporate issuers.
